### Summaries — Weekly podium, monthly champion, live standings

### Get all week summaries (podium history)
GET {{host}}/api/summaries/weeks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get all month summaries (monthly champion history)
GET {{host}}/api/summaries/months
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get current month live standings (in-progress rankings)
GET {{host}}/api/summaries/current-month
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
